summary: This code creates a model base class implementing NSCoding protocol, with initializer, equality checker, and status setter. It initializes objects using decode methods from a decoder and encodes properties for archiving.

details.comment: TOModelBase.m: Implementation of a model base class, including initializer, self identifier, equality checker, and status setter.

This code implements a model class that conforms to NSCoding protocol. It initializes the object properties using decode methods from a decoder in its init method, and encodes the object's properties for archiving with encodeWithCoder method.
